{"id":"8095","name":"bright-early-get-this-show-on-the-road-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Get This Show On The Road Edition","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2012-02-27T11:45:00-06:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/tomfrundle/6915039203/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"blank\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-8097 aligncenter\" title=\"Screen Shot 2012-02-27 at 11.56.08 AM\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Screen-Shot-2012-02-27-at-11.56.08-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"496\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville.&#xA0;<a href=\"http://nashvillecitypaper.com/content/city-news/state-gop-primary-shapes-knock-down-drag-out-affair?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+NashvilleCityPaper-LatestNews+%28Nashville+City+Paper+-+Latest+News%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessee&#x2019;s SuperTuesday Republican primary is shaping up to be quite the event</a> after a Vanderbilt University poll released over the weekend showed <a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=34519\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Rick Santorum with a significant lead</a>. Santorum made several campaign appearances in east Tennessee over the weekend, and <a href=\"http://www.usatoday.com/news/politics/story/2012-02-26/santorum-poll-tennessee/53255538/1\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.usatoday.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Newt Gingrich is campaigning in Nashville today</a>. Speaking of voting: <a href=\"http://www.nashville.gov/vote/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashville.gov&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tomorrow is your last day to early vote</a> if you want to avoid the crowds next Tuesday, so get thee to a pollery ASAP (if that&#x2019;s your thing, of course).</p><ul><li><strong>Nashville noms</strong>. <a href=\"http://nashvillepost.com/news/2012/2/26/the_food_biz_national_perch\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillepost.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The James Beard Foundation dished out some lovin&#x2019; on Nashville restaurants and chefs last week</a>, nominating The Catbird Seat for best new restaurant and chefs Tandy Wilson (City House) and Tyler Brown (Capitol Grille) for best chef in the Southeast.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/17013821/suspicious-powder-found-at-al-gores-office\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">More &#x201C;suspicious powder&#x201D; was found in Nashville on Friday</a>, this time in former Vice President Al Gore&#x2019;s office in Green Hills &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/17011632/man-puts-baby-on-craigslist-for-850\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">A Clarksville man landed in jail for advertising a baby for sale on Craigslist</a>, but don&#x2019;t worry, it was just a joke &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20120224/NEWS01/302240130/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Green Hills will get a new Mexican restaurant this summer</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://nashvillepost.com/blogs/postbusiness/2012/2/24/vince_gill_exits_mca\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillepost.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Vince Gill has parted ways with MCA Records</a> &#x2026; <a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/nashville/news/2012/02/24/permits-new-york-company-brow-art.html?ana=RSS&amp;s=article_search&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bizj_nashville+%28Nashville+Business+Journal%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.bizjournals.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">New York &amp; Co, Brow Art 23 (we don&#x2019;t even want to know), Subway, Solitaire the Diamond Outlet and Motherhood Maternity</a> are the latest updates to the Opry Mills roster &#x2026; A <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/17011944/bass-pro-shops-accident\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">family of three got trapped under a boat at Bass Pro this weekend</a>, thanks to a rogue Ford F-150 &#x2026; The <a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/nashville/morning_call/2012/02/titans-raising-some-ticket-prices.html?ana=RSS&amp;s=article_search&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bizj_nashville+%28Nashville+Business+Journal%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.bizjournals.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Titans are jacking up the price of lower-bowl tickets by $6</a> &#x2026;&#xA0;<a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/nashville/morning_call/2012/02/tennessee-documentary-wins-oscar.html?ana=RSS&amp;s=article_search&amp;utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+bizj_nashville+%28Nashville+Business+Journal%29\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.bizjournals.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Congrats to &#x201C;Undefeated,&#x201D;</a> a Memphis-made film that took home the Best Documentary Oscar at the Academy Awards last night.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/tomfrundle/6915039203/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tom C Frundle</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/11/13/were-takin-this-show-on-the-road-barcamp-memphis/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: We&#x2019;re Takin&#x2019; This Show On The Road: BarCamp Memphis\">We&#x2019;re Takin&#x2019; This Show On The Road: BarCamp Memphis</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}